Social-split marker (2026-06-10).

Series in a directory containing this file publish to the website only:
publish-next-day gets --skip-bsky --skip-x from daily-ops. Mastodon
still mirrors them via the RSS mirror (zero-effort channel).

Why: our Bluesky engagement data shows Accountability posts average
7.0 engagements vs 2.3 for Legislation explainers, and follower count
dropped during the mirror-everything high-volume week. Evergreen
explainers are SEO inventory (search is our top acquisition channel),
not social inventory.

Delete this file to restore full social mirroring for the series.
